{{ define "settings_sso_content" }}<section class="space-y-6"><div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4"><div><h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white">Single Sign-On</h2><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">SSO can be configured externally via a reverse proxy or OAuth2 provider.</p></div></div><div class="cq-panel p-7"><p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">SSO not configured. 🍃</p><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">ChronoQueue self-hosted does not include built-in SSO. Use a reverse proxy (nginx, Caddy) or OAuth2 proxy to add authentication in front of this interface.</p></div></section>{{ end }}
